data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Welcome to our app! To start, please pick an example or enter a file path into the top left dropdown button. Alternatively, just start typing commands into the input section in the middle! You can choose to load a file for editing by pressing the "Load File" button after having typed the path, or you can skip this step and run it directly from the file by just typing the file path.
Please follow the formatting rules for the commands, such as not leaving an extra space at the end of a line, as doing so will be counted as invalid input. You may use either spaces or line ends to seperate commands, but not both.
